{"tid":991383,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現女朋友寫緊遺書..","createTime":"2019-01-22T10:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T11:01:17.000Z","uid":207497,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"29fd3e248c0c7380441ffdad6626f61997381605","tid":991383,"uid":207497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:45:09.000Z","msg":"我今日上左女朋友屋企<br />\n發現佢個櫃有個好靚嘅盒<br />\n我就諗住打開睇下係放乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一打開就見到有幾封信<br />\n每封都有一個人嘅名<br />\n我個名都有係到<br />\n唔知點解我個下靜係諗到13 Reasons why <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我拆開左封寫比我嘅信<br />\n佢好似未寫完<br />\n我睇得好急靜係見到中間有句<br />\n唔好傷心 對唔住 要離開之類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽到佢行緊入黎我就放返原位<br />\n<br />\n我應該點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔知應該直接問佢好定曲線開解佢<br />\n好驚佢真係離開我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731ac51cb52402f4a909d2829bb97953438e70a1","tid":991383,"uid":224107,"like":5,"dislike":68,"score":-63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: green;\">帽事既</span>"},{"pid":"956f62a7bd96742c23fd59b4947b9274d221f022","tid":991383,"uid":53379,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問下佢最近係咪唔開心"},{"pid":"e5eb398fc07364910209a3e0b281354e07f8dd91","tid":991383,"uid":148609,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:51:20.000Z","msg":"我都會寫定遺書 揀埋遺照<br />\n幾時死呢啲野話唔埋<br />\n廢事有啲野冇機會再講<br />\n不過唔知你女友係咪咁<br />\n如果你地平時係乜都會傾咪問吓囉"},{"pid":"8d1685cb91428f4829537c014e2c2e2c6d16e440","tid":991383,"uid":207497,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"q